      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic and dependable ride! It's in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience for its next owner. The interior is clean and comfortable, making it a great choice for daily commutes or weekend adventures. It\u2019s a solid vehicle that\u2019s ready to hit the road with you!",
