      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been well-loved, with just the usual minor signs of use you'd expect. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin!",
