    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit boasts a documented Double VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's known stress points. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile feedback, channeling torque through a limited-slip differential. Performance is enhanced by a refreshed cooling system and Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension maintain optimal geometry under load. The individual throttle bodies offer instantaneous response, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM limit. A mechanically robust example ready for the B-roads.",
