    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition for its mileage. Finished in a timeless Volcano Grey Metallic, the exterior retains a deep gloss, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior is pristine and smoke-free; the seat bolsters show only very light softening, and all electronics, including the premium Bose surround sound, function perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It features a complete service history from authorized centers, with the most recent major service completed just 3,000 miles ago. The turbocharged V6 delivers smooth, consistent power, and the PDK transmission shifts flawlessly. The tires are matching Pirellis with ample tread remaining. It\u2019s a reliable, spirited performer ready for its next owner.",
